@startuml
title MedBlockDFL System – Sequence Diagram (Single FL Round)

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontSize 12
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #F0F4FF
    BorderColor #2563EB
    FontSize 11
}

skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #87CEEB
    BorderColor #1E88E5
    FontSize 11
}

' === PARTICIPANTS ===
actor "Client" as Client
participant "DAVS" as DAVS
participant "PBFT" as PBFT
participant "Aggregator" as Agg
participant "Blockchain" as BC

autonumber

== 1. Local Training ==
Client -> Client: Train local model
Client -> Client: Compute gradients

== 2. Gradient Sketching ==
Client -> Client: Create gradient sketch
Client -> DAVS: Broadcast sketch
activate DAVS

== 3. DAVS Selection ==
DAVS -> DAVS: Calculate representativeness
DAVS -> DAVS: Select top-k verifiers
DAVS -> PBFT: Form committee
deactivate DAVS
activate PBFT

== 4. PBFT Consensus ==
Client -> PBFT: Submit gradients
PBFT -> PBFT: Pre-Prepare
PBFT -> PBFT: Prepare
PBFT -> PBFT: Commit (2f+1)
PBFT -> Agg: Validated updates
deactivate PBFT

== 5. Aggregation ==
activate Agg
Agg -> Agg: Robust aggregation
Agg -> BC: Commit model
deactivate Agg
activate BC

== 6. Blockchain ==
BC -> BC: Create block
BC -> BC: Append to chain
BC -> Client: Broadcast updated model
deactivate BC

@enduml
